KPL/IK

INSIGHT Auxiliary Instrument Kernel
===============================================================================

   This Instrument Kernel (IK) file contains Field-Of-View (FOV)
   definitions for a few INSIGHT instruments and structures that don't
   yet or will never have their own IKs.


